title: AWS Snowcone Launch - A Small, Rugged, and Secure Edge Computing and Data Transfer Device (:30)
description:
AWS Snowcone is the smallest member of the AWS Snow Family of edge computing and data transfer devices. Snowcone is portable, rugged, and secure – small and light enough to fit in a backpack, and able to withstand harsh environments. 

Customers use Snowcone to deploy applications at the edge, and to collect data, process it locally, and move it to AWS either offline (by shipping the device to AWS) or online (by using AWS DataSync on Snowcone to send the data to AWS over the network).

Learn more about AWS Snowcone at https://go.aws/3d16fx6
